data.value: Gomoku , also called Five in a Row, is an abstract strategy board game. Gomoku may also be played as a paper-and-pencil game. The game is known in several countries under different names. By using Caro, it's is not only easy but convenient for you to play alone or with your friend without prepare board or paper, and have some speacial feature to make the game more fun.
